### ============================================
### GHAS Alerts - APIs REST directas
### ============================================
###
### Endpoints para consultar alertas de GHAS
### de forma individual (sin filtro por properties).
###
### Para filtrado por custom properties, usa
### el script get_alerts_by_properties.py
### ============================================

### Variables de configuración
@token = {{$dotenv GITHUB_TOKEN_DEMO_03}}
@org = {{$dotenv GITHUB_ORG}}
@repo = ghas-demo-mobile-android-kotlin
@baseUrl = https://api.github.com
@apiVersion = 2022-11-28

### =========================================
### 🔍 Code Scanning
### =========================================

### Alertas de code scanning de toda la org
### Filtros: state, severity, tool_name, sort, direction
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/code-scanning/alerts
    ?per_page=30
    &state=open
    &sort=created
    &direction=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### Alertas de code scanning de un repo
### Filtros adicionales: ref (branch), tool_name, severity
GET {{baseUrl}}/repos/{{org}}/{{repo}}/code-scanning/alerts
    ?per_page=30
    &state=open
    &severity=high
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### =========================================
### 🔑 Secret Scanning
### =========================================

### Alertas de secret scanning de toda la org
### Filtros: state, secret_type, resolution, sort, direction
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/secret-scanning/alerts
    ?per_page=30
    &state=open
    &sort=created
    &direction=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### Alertas de secret scanning de un repo
GET {{baseUrl}}/repos/{{org}}/{{repo}}/secret-scanning/alerts
    ?per_page=30
    &state=open
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### =========================================
### 📦 Dependabot
### =========================================

### Alertas de Dependabot de toda la org
### Filtros: state, severity, ecosystem, package, scope, sort, direction
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/dependabot/alerts
    ?per_page=30
    &state=open
    &sort=created
    &direction=desc
    &severity=critical
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### Alertas de Dependabot de un repo
GET {{baseUrl}}/repos/{{org}}/{{repo}}/dependabot/alerts
    ?per_page=30
    &state=open
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### =========================================
### 📊 Filtrar repos por custom properties
### (para luego obtener alertas de cada uno)
### =========================================

### Obtener repos mobile
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/values
    ?repository_query=props.application_type:mobile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### Obtener repos mobile Android
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/values
    ?repository_query=props.application_type:mobile props.mobile_platform:android
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}
